.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, iced-tea
There are 2 different favourite colors: white, fuchsia
The people have 2 different jobs:  police-officer, teacher
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: indie, r&b
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cricket, water-polo
2 different pets are kept: lizard, mouse
House: art-deco, wooden
1. the teacher is on the right of the person who likes fuchsia##1
2. the owner of the mouse is the wooden house##1
3. the art-deco house is on the left of the fan of indie##1
4. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking almond-milk is the owner of the lizard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Beverage      | almond-milk    | iced-tea |
| Color         | fuchsia        | white  |
| Job           | police-officer | teacher  |
| Music-Genre   | r&b            | indie    |
| Sport   | cricket     | water-polo   |
| Pet           | lizard         | mouse    |
| House     | art-deco           | wooden      |

