3. the person driving the quad-bike is the person who growsballoon-flower##1
4. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
5. the person driving the ship is the person watching adventure movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |
| Beverage      | soy-milk   | hot-chocolate |
| Food          | kiwi       | blueberry     |
| Flower           | azalea  | balloon-flower   |
| Music-Genre   | rock       | pop           |
| Cigar   | tiparillo | davidoff    |
| Movie-Genre         | adventure  | martial-arts      |
| Transport     | ship       | quad-bike     |

 